headline: A Look Back at Heavy Transportation Equipment Stocks’ Q4 Earnings: PACCAR (NASDAQ:PCAR) Vs The Rest Of The Pack
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how PACCAR (NASDAQ:PCAR) and the rest of the heavy transportation equipment stocks fared in Q4.
